snippet.title: Superliminal - Steam Launch Trailer. New Features!
snippet.description:
Wishlist here: https://store.steampowered.com/app/1049410/Superliminal/

Superliminal is coming to Steam on November 5th, 2020!
 
Some new features include:
- Challenge Mode
- Developer Commentary
- (Very Experimental) Steam workshop support
